{
  "id": "69c6cb31267ad1f715225a5d",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:難しい言葉を多用する",
  "created": 1774635852,
  "updated": 1774635865,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c6cb31267ad1f715225a5d",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:難しい言葉を多用する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635852,
      "updated": 1774635852
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4b0000000000ae5c12",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635852,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c13",
      "text": "「はいどーも！本日のテーマは〜“難しい言葉を多用する”について！いやもうさ、厨二ワード大会って感じ？ｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c14",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c15",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c16",
      "text": "「正確には“過度な専門用語の濫用”だね。コミュニケーションコストが増大する現象とも言える。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c17",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c18",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c19",
      "text": "「でたでた、もう始まってるｗ “コミュニケーションコスト”ってつまり“会話むずくなってダルい”ってことね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c1a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c1b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c1c",
      "text": "「概ねその理解で問題ない。翻訳精度が高い。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c1e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c1f",
      "text": "「難しい言葉には、どこか響きの美しさや奥ゆかしさもございますけれど……伝わらなければ、まるで閉ざされた書庫のようでございますね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c21",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c22",
      "text": "「お、あやの例えオシャレ〜。でもさ、“閉ざされた書庫”ってつまり“読めない本棚”ってことでしょ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c24",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c25",
      "text": "「ええ、そうとも言えますね。誰かと分かち合うための言葉が、かえって壁になってしまうのは、少し寂しいことでございます。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c27",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c28",
      "text": "「要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c29",
      "text": " 1. 難解語は情報密度が高い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c2a",
      "text": " 2. しかし受信側の知識に依存する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c2b",
      "text": " 3. 結果、共有知識が不足すると意味が欠落する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c2c",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c2e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c2f",
      "text": "「急にプレゼン始まったｗ スライドどこ？ｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c31",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c32",
      "text": "「脳内に表示してほしい。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c34",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c35",
      "text": "「無茶ぶりｗｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c37",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c38",
      "text": "「けれど、りかさんのおっしゃる通り、言葉とは受け取る方の心に寄り添ってこそ意味を成しますね。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c3a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c3b",
      "text": "「そういう意見もある。補足すると、専門用語は“圧縮アルゴリズム”のようなものだ。長い説明を短くできる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c3d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c3e",
      "text": "「圧縮アルゴリズム…えっと、“長文をギュッとまとめる魔法”ってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c40",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c41",
      "text": "「いい表現だ。まさにそれ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c43",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c44",
      "text": "「まあ、素敵な言い換えでございますね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c46",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c47",
      "text": "「でしょ〜？でもさ、その魔法ってさ、レベル足りないと解けない呪文みたいじゃない？初心者お断り的なｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c49",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c4a",
      "text": "「興味深い比喩だ。専門用語は“前提知識という鍵”が必要になる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c4b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c4c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c4d",
      "text": "「鍵を持たぬ方には、扉が開かぬのですね……。それでは少し、寂しい世界に感じられます。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c4f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c50",
      "text": "「そうそう！だからさ、日常会話で“パラダイムシフトが〜”とか言われても、“急に何のボス戦？”ってなるしｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c51",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c52",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c53",
      "text": "「パラダイムシフト＝“考え方が大きく変わること”だね。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c55",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c56",
      "text": "「はい翻訳ありがとうｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c58",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c59",
      "text": "「ですが、難しい言葉を選ぶ方にも、きっと理由がございますよね。正確に伝えたい、というお気持ちがあるのではないでしょうか。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c5b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c5c",
      "text": "「その通り。精度を優先すると語彙は専門化する。例えば“バグ”と“仕様”は厳密には異なる概念だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c5d",
      "text": "参考：https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/バグ 」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c5f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c60",
      "text": "「リンク貼ったｗ さすが技術担当ｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c62",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c63",
      "text": "「エビデンスは常に提示する主義だ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c65",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c66",
      "text": "「丁寧で素晴らしい姿勢でございますね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c68",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c69",
      "text": "「でもさ、結論どうする？難しい言葉って使うべき？封印すべき？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c6b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c6c",
      "text": "「結論を提示する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c6d",
      "text": " 専門的な場では有効",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c6e",
      "text": " 一般会話では適度に翻訳する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c6f",
      "text": " 相手の知識レベルに適応する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c70",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c72",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c73",
      "text": "「お〜バランス型！つまり“空気読んで言葉選べ”ってことね！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c75",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c76",
      "text": "「簡潔で的確だ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c78",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c79",
      "text": "「言葉とは、相手を思う心のかたちでございますね。難しさよりも、伝えようとする優しさが大切なのかもしれません。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c7b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c7c",
      "text": "「いいこと言う〜！じゃあ今日のまとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c7d",
      "text": "“難しい言葉はカッコいいけど、そのままだと通じないから、ちゃんと翻訳しよう！”ってことで！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c7f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c80",
      "text": "「補足。“翻訳力”は重要なスキルだ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c82",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c83",
      "text": "「よし、みんな今日から“日常会話翻訳士”ね！ｗ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c85",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c86",
      "text": "「なんだか楽しそうな響きでございますね。（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6cb4d0000000000ae5c87",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774635853,
      "updated": 1774635853
    },
